      <title>特朗普撤回关税威胁 人民币升值</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/yuan-gains-with-china-proxies-as-trump-dials-back-tariff-threats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有迹象表明特朗普总统正在收回对中国出口产品征收更高关税的威胁，人民币随之上涨，与对中国经济敏感的资产一起上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/yuan-gains-with-china-proxies-as-trump-dials-back-tariff-threats</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 02:28:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国收益率曲线趋平，中国人民银行成为焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/china-s-flatter-yield-curve-is-putting-focus-on-pboc-bond-buying</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国人民银行决定暂停购买债券，这加剧了短期利率的上升和收益率曲线的趋平，引发人们对央行可能恢复购买政府债券的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/china-s-flatter-yield-curve-is-putting-focus-on-pboc-bond-buying</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 00:44:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡房价上涨，租金持平，但路边谈话增多</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/singapore-home-prices-jump-2-3-as-curb-speculation-mounts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[分析师预测，新加坡政府今年可能会出手干预，给房地产市场降温，但 2024 年最后一个季度，新加坡房价的上涨速度与最初的预期一致。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/singapore-home-prices-jump-2-3-as-curb-speculation-mounts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 00:42:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
